      "role": "user",
      "content": "small steps? man, i'm talking millions in debt. people i worked with for years are looking at me like i'm some kind of criminal. i can't just \"self-care\" my way out of this level of humiliation. it feels like the world just closed in on me and there's no way out that doesn't involve everyone seeing me as a total failure.",
