      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just feel like there's no version of the future where this doesn't follow me. every time i close my eyes i just see the faces of the people i let down. it feels like the only way to actually stop the noise and the shame is for everything to just... end. like, is it even worth trying to fix something this broken?",
